@token = bwpEG_RpQ4QFoqmO9sdDlD_OumUNxVAEgJRHTeAMTqk=

### Registar um novo utilizador
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "teste2",
  "email": "test2@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}

### Obter token de autenticação
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@gmail.com",
  "password": "minhaSenhaSegura"
}



### Criar um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "lobbyHostId": 0,
  "name": "Lobby Teste",
  "description": "Descrição do lobby",
  "minPlayers": 2,
  "maxPlayers": 6,
  "rounds": 5,
  "ante": 100
}

### Listar todos os lobbies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies

### Obter lobby por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1

### Juntar-se a um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": {
    "id": 2,
    "username": "jogador2"
  }
}

### Sair de um lobby
POST http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": {
    "id": 2,
    "username": "jogador2"
  }
}

### Listar jogadores de um lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/players

### Obter host do lobby
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lobbies/1/host
